          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7HReHpCY-K2j6MRntwp5BfKE8qLtv7Ch68lvXl68Ki9gGwTvZGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I am grateful for the chance to be alive. Two years ago I had the kidney transplant surgery and can't be more happier. Special thanks to Dr. Johnathan Berger,  all nurses and doctors who were next to me during my treatment in the hospital. Great people \ud83d\udc4f,  great  facility. God bless you all. \ud83d\ude4f",
